arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	-- Find the Actors in Prefab: QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_Contents
	idTaissaSwamp = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_NPCTaissa")[1]
	tGhostSpawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_GhostAmbushSpawners")
	
	-- Enable Ghost Spawners
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tGhostSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
	end
	
	--Taissa enabled and posed
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idTaissaSwamp)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(idTaissaSwamp, animsetTaissaGround)
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idTaissaSwamp, "AnimKey_Sick_Prone_OnBack")
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(sConvoTaissa01_T01a, idTaissaSwamp)
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(sConvoTaissa01_T01c, idTaissaSwamp)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(sConvoTaissa01_T01c)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idTaissaSwamp, fxAndarielLaugh)
	
	for i, idChainSpawner in ipairs(tChainSpawners2) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idChainSpawner, false)
	end
	
	for i, idHutSpawner in ipairs(tHutSpawners2) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idHutSpawner, false)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.1)
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idEscapeLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorNPC, "runloc")[1]
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(idActorNPC)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idActorNPC, idEscapeLoc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idActorNPC, 1.0)
	
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	--References
	idTaissaSwamp = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_NPCTaissa")[1]
	tChainSpawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_NPCChainsSpawners")
	tHutSpawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_HutSpawners")
	tChainSpawners2 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_NPCChainsSpawners2")
	tHutSpawners2 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Verge_Taissa_01_Cellar_HutSpawners2")

	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idTaissaSwamp, sConvoTaissa01_T01a)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idTaissaSwamp)
	
	--Taissa Bark
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(sConvoTaissa01_T01b, idTaissaSwamp)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(sConvoTaissa01_T01b)
	Hydra.EventSend("SpawnGhosts")
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	-- Impact the player if they are too close!
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idTaissaSwamp, 10)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idTaissaSwamp, sDemonicBurst, true)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idTaissaSwamp, sPowerKnockBack)
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.10)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idTaissaSwamp, fxAndarielLaugh)
		
	--Chains spawner
	for i, idChainSpawner in ipairs(tChainSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idChainSpawner, false)
	end
	
	for i, idHutSpawner in ipairs(tHutSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idHutSpawner, false)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.1)
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(idTaissaSwamp, "AnimKey_Sick_Prone_OnBack_Getup", "AnimKey_Sick_Standing_Idle")
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idTaissaSwamp)
	
end
